text: Virgil Neagoe (born 3 July 1970) is a Romanian ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1992 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Romania Category:Ski jumpers at the 1992 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
